I'm sorry to sounds kind of rude; I'm really not, it's just that I get SO MANY useless and ridiculous messgages when trading a high-end firearm that I'd rather not get stuck in text message conversations with people trying to convince me that their DPMS AR-15 w NC-Star scope and a Ruger LCP is an equal trade.  Anyway, this rifle started life as a heavey barrel short action .308 Savage 10FP LEO (law enforcement model) and then a free-float Choate tactical sniper stock was added and the Accuracy International bottom metal (the thing that allows you to use detachable box mags) was installed. This rifle takes Accuary International .308 mags. Yes, I know they're expensive as hell (about $80 to $100 each) so I'm including 3 of them (two 5rd mags and one 10rd mag and yes they're all marked "AI"). One of the 5rd mags is painted and the other two are mint.  The paint on the rifle is just Krylon spray paint. The original color of the stock underneath is black and OD green. The scope is a Vortex Viper PST 4-16X50. This scope has tactical turrets and an illuminated reticle. It also is a first focal plane reticle scope so that's super sexy.  The bipod is an authentic Harris 9" HBLMS bipod and is included.  Again, I'm only looking for trades, not cash.  Keep in mind that the bottom metal and 3 mags are alone worth $550ish so please don't offer me your Glock .40 as a striagt trade. Again, trying not to be a jerk but I get a lot of silly trade offers. Also, the rough value of this package is hard to pin down and I'm certainly not trying to get every penny out of it that I put into it (that'd be silly) but the scope is roughly $700, the bipod about $110, the bottom metal and mags, as I mentioned are about $550, the rifle + tactical stock is about $1,200 so please just keep in mind the rough value when making a trade offer.  Trades can be anything. I'm open to whatever and I enjoy seeing what offers roll in. Please just keep them reasonable and PLEASE include the trade offer in your first message to me. I can follow up from there but I've never seen the point in the people who message me with "Intersted, message me". Again, please include where you're located too when you're offering a trade. I'd trade this for one single high end gun or multiple guns. Just let me know what you have, where you're at and roughly when you might be available to meet.
